quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  22,19,"ЖҒee Й—oo Й—iЙ—o ko wennjondirЙ“e, Й“e wennjondirii fii Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“en yedduЙ“e non, taЖҙanoyte Й“e conci immorde e Yiite fatuЙ—am yuppee ka dow ko'e maЙ“Й“e"
  22,20,HiЙ—am honciniree(hayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi maЙ“Й“e e guri Й—in kadi
  22,21,No woodani Й“oole immorde e njamndi
  22,22,"Tuma kala Й“e faandii yaltugol nder ton immorde e suno, Й“e ruttee e nder magge, [Й“e wiвҖҷanee:] meeЙ—ee Lette sumoowe ngen"
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naada Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golle moЖҙЖҙi Й—in Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji canЙ—i Й—in, Й“e cuЙ—iree nder ton immorde jawe kanЕӢe e lu'ulu'uuje koltu maЙ“Й“e on nder ton ko hariire. @Corrected"
  22,24,"ЖҒe fewnaama faade e ko laaЙ“i immorde e konngol ngol, Й“e fewnaa kadi faade e Laawol Yettiniingol ngol"
  22,25,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e hiЙ“e faddaade gaayi Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Men waЙ—ani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en, no fota ter ГұiiЙ“uЙ—o on e mayre e liigotooЙ—o on. Kala faalaaЙ—o ooГұorde e mayre tooГұe, Men meeЙ—inay mo immorde e Lepte muusuЙ—e"
  22,26,"E tuma nde Men Jippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Men Daali:] Wata a kafidu e Am hay e huunde, laЙ“Й“in Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotooЙ“e Й“en e darotooЙ“e Й“en [juula] e ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e sujja Й“en"
  22,27,"Noddin e yimЙ“e Й“en fii Hajju ngun, Й“e aray e maaЙ—a ko Й“e seppooЙ“e e dow kala Й—ehiimba reedu, Й“e aray immorde e kala laawol woЙ—Й—ungol"
  22,28,"Fii yo Й“e seedo nafoore maЙ“Й“e, Й“e jaЕӢtoo Innde Alla e nder ГұalЙ—i anndaaЙ—i e dow ko O arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i, Гұaamee e majji, Гұamminon kadi baaso Й“illiiЙ—o on"
  22,29,"Refti yo Й“e ittu tuundi maЙ“Й“e ndin, yo Й“e humnu takke maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yo Й“e wanngo Suudu rimdinaa- dun"
  22,30,"ЖҠum [ko yamiraЙ—on], kala mawninЙ—o Hurumji Alla Й—in haray Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere makko ka Joomi makko. Daginanaama on neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, si wonaa kon ko janngaa e taweede mo'on, woЙ—Й—itee soЙ“udi Й—in immorde e sanamuuji, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on kadi konngol fenaande ngol"
  22,31,"NewaniiЙ“e Alla Й“e wanaali sirkanooЙ“e Mo, kala sirkanЙ—o Alla no wa'ita wa si o uuyu immorde ka kammu sonndu biftoo mo maaЙ—um henndu ndun ruuyida e makko [naЙ“a] e nokkure woЙ—Й—unde"
  22,32,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo hollii] kala mawninЙ—o Maandeeji Alla Й—in, pellet Й—um, ko e kulol Й“erЙ—e Й—en jeyaa"
  22,33,"No woodani on e majji nafaaji haa e dummunne innaaЙ—o, refti nokku majji on ko ka Suudu Ndimuru"
  22,34,"Men waЙ—anii kala mofte laawol fii yo Й“e jaЕӢto Innde Alla e dow ko O arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i. ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto ko Kanko jebbilatoЙ—on, weltinir Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en"
  22,35,"ЖҒen [tawЙ“e] si Alla jaЕӢtaama Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hulay, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e dow kon ko heЙ“i Й“e e ГұinnooЙ“e Julde nden hiЙ“e nafka goЙ—Й—um e ko Men arsiki Й“e kon"
  22,36,"E gelooЙ—i [fayЙ—i] Й—in Men waЙ—anii on Й—i jeyaaЙ—um e Maandeeji Alla no woodani on e majji moЖҙЖҙere, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko Й—i saffiniiЙ—i si becce majji Й—en yanii haray Гұaamee immorde e majji Гұamminon kadi yonndiniiЙ—o e weeЙ“itotooЙ—o, ko wano nii, Men eltirani on Й—i belajo'o onon on jarnay"
  22,37,"Hewtoytaa Alla tebbuuli majji wanaa ЖҙiiЖҙe majji kadi, kono hewtoy Mo kulol ngol immorde e mo'on. Ko wano nii O eltani on Й—i fii yo on mawnin Alla e dow ko O fewni on kon, weltin moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“en"